{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RqrLyjZ5ifCDVt2KqCrTV6","type":"tool_result","content":"    50→- Sprint state reading and aggregation (move to `index.ts`)\n    51→- URL construction for observability dashboards (move to `endpoints.ts`)\n    52→- Human-readable table/tree formatting (move to `formatters.ts`)\n    53→- Story drill-down with AC status, retry history (move to `drill-down.ts`)\n    54→\n    55→Note: `src/modules/sprint/drill-down.ts` already exists. The new `src/modules/status/drill-down.ts` handles status-command-specific presentation, while `src/modules/sprint/drill-down.ts` handles sprint-level story detail. They may need to be reconciled -- check for overlap.\n    56→\n    57→`buildScopedEndpoints()` must produce identical URLs to the current implementation. Write a comparison test.\n    58→\n    59→## Files to Change\n    60→\n    61→- `src/modules/status/index.ts` — Create. `getStatus()` reads sprint-state.json and aggregates, `formatOutput()` dispatches to formatters\n    62→- `src/modules/status/formatters.ts` — Create. Table and tree formatting for human-readable output, JSON formatting\n    63→- `src/modules/status/endpoints.ts` — Create. `buildScopedEndpoints()` URL builders for Victoria/ELK/remote endpoints\n    64→- `src/modules/status/drill-down.ts` — Create. Story detail view with AC status, retry history, timeline\n    65→- `src/commands/status.ts` — Gut to <100 lines: arg parsing, call status module, format output\n    66→- `src/modules/status/__tests__/endpoints.test.ts` — Create. Verify URL generation matches current implementation\n    67→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a74f233b-d75f-4731-af98-d5f8de661326","uuid":"9af213c8-941c-42e1-a320-1577183b17da","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:32:48.641Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/12-3-move-status-logic-to-module.md","content":"- Sprint state reading and aggregation (move to `index.ts`)\n- URL construction for observability dashboards (move to `endpoints.ts`)\n- Human-readable table/tree formatting (move to `formatters.ts`)\n- Story drill-down with AC status, retry history (move to `drill-down.ts`)\n\nNote: `src/modules/sprint/drill-down.ts` already exists. The new `src/modules/status/drill-down.ts` handles status-command-specific presentation, while `src/modules/sprint/drill-down.ts` handles sprint-level story detail. They may need to be reconciled -- check for overlap.\n\n`buildScopedEndpoints()` must produce identical URLs to the current implementation. Write a comparison test.\n\n## Files to Change\n\n- `src/modules/status/index.ts` — Create. `getStatus()` reads sprint-state.json and aggregates, `formatOutput()` dispatches to formatters\n- `src/modules/status/formatters.ts` — Create. Table and tree formatting for human-readable output, JSON formatting\n- `src/modules/status/endpoints.ts` — Create. `buildScopedEndpoints()` URL builders for Victoria/ELK/remote endpoints\n- `src/modules/status/drill-down.ts` — Create. Story detail view with AC status, retry history, timeline\n- `src/commands/status.ts` — Gut to <100 lines: arg parsing, call status module, format output\n- `src/modules/status/__tests__/endpoints.test.ts` — Create. Verify URL generation matches current implementation\n","numLines":18,"startLine":50,"totalLines":67}}}
